trans-unit.source: Provides methods for writing to a document referenced by a symbol store.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder metoder for å skrive til et dokument refererer til et symbol lager.

trans-unit.source: A document is defined by a URL and a document type GUID.
trans-unit.target: Et dokument er definert av en URL-adresse og en dokumenttype GUID.

trans-unit.source: Optionally, the document source can be stored in the symbol store.
trans-unit.target: Eventuelt kan kilden dokumentet lagres i butikken symbolet.

trans-unit.source: Releases the resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Frigir ressursene som brukes av den gjeldende forekomsten av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Called by the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter.Dispose*> and <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter.Finalize*> methods to release the managed and unmanaged resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Kalles av den <> </> *> og <> </> *> metoder for å frigjøre behandlet ressursene som brukes i den gjeldende forekomsten av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This method is called only by the public <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter.Dispose%2A> and <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter.Finalize%2A> methods; do not call this method directly.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles bare av offentlig <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter.Dispose%2A>og <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter.Finalize%2A>metoder; ikke kalle denne metoden direkte.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter.Finalize%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre ressurser behandlet. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Releases unmanaged resources and performs other cleanup operations before the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter"></xref> is reclaimed by garbage collection.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressurser og til å utføre andre operasjoner for opprydding før den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymDocumentWriter"> </xref> gode av datasanering.

trans-unit.source: Application code should not call this method; an object's `Finalize` method is automatically invoked during garbage collection, unless finalization by the garbage collector has been disabled by a call to the <xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Applikasjons-koden kan ikke kalle denne metoden. et objekts `Finalize` metode startes automatisk under datasanering, med mindre finalization av saneringsoppsamlingen er deaktivert av et kall til den <xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%2A>metoden.</xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%2A>
